SubjectAuthorization to sign certificates to facilitate the registration of Maa-nulth First Nation Lands under the British Columbia Land Titles Act.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development and Federal Interlocutor for Métis and Non-Status Indians to sign certificates to facilitate the registration of Maa-nulth First Nation Lands, as necessary, described in the Maa-nulth First Nations Final Agreement under the British Columbia Land Titles Act.
